title: S3 EP15: Tuesday the 17th with James Roday Rodriguez
description:
This week, Maggie & Tim are joined by Shawn Spencer himself, Mr. James Roday Rodriguez! Together, they talk about Season 3 Episode 15: Tuesday the 17th. The perfect Friday the 13th spoof! James talks about his directorial debut and what it was like to write, direct and act in this amazing episode.
